director.name: 黎刹·曼托瓦尼 Rizal Mantovani

introduction: Mumun wants to marry her fiancé, Juned. But, before marriage, she loses her life. Unfortunately, Mumun's pocong rope is neglected to be removed by Husein, the gravedigger. Mumun becomes a pocong and brings havoc to the people. Juned, who still couldn't let go of her departure, couldn't accept she was called Pocong Mumun. Pocong Mumun also haunts Mimin, Mumun's twin sister, who has to return to treat her parents' grief.
